{"data":{"allPostTitles":{"edges":[{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/color-picker/accessibility/","gcse":"014729256687841406486:qzbiyd0sri4"}}},{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/color-picker/getting-started/","gcse":"014729256687841406486:qzbiyd0sri4"}}},{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/color-picker/","gcse":"014729256687841406486:qzbiyd0sri4"}}},{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/color-picker/mode-and-value/","gcse":"014729256687841406486:qzbiyd0sri4"}}},{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/slider/accessibility/","gcse":"014729256687841406486:qzbiyd0sri4"}}},{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/slider/format/","gcse":"014729256687841406486:qzbiyd0sri4"}}},{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/slider/getting-started/","gcse":"014729256687841406486:qzbiyd0sri4"}}},{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/slider/limits/","gcse":"014729256687841406486:qzbiyd0sri4"}}},{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/slider/orientation/","gcse":"014729256687841406486:qzbiyd0sri4"}}},{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/slider/ticks/","gcse":"014729256687841406486:qzbiyd0sri4"}}},{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/slider/tooltip/","gcse":"014729256687841406486:qzbiyd0sri4"}}},{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/slider/types/","gcse":"014729256687841406486:qzbiyd0sri4"}}},{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/color-picker/how-to/customize-color-picker/","gcse":"014729256687841406486:qzbiyd0sri4"}}},{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/color-picker/how-to/disable-color-picker/","gcse":"014729256687841406486:qzbiyd0sri4"}}},{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/color-picker/how-to/hide-control-buttons/","gcse":"014729256687841406486:qzbiyd0sri4"}}},{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/color-picker/how-to/render-palette-alone/","gcse":"014729256687841406486:qzbiyd0sri4"}}}]},"postBySlug":{"html":"<h1 id=\"hide-control-buttons\"><a href=\"#hide-control-buttons\" aria-hidden class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Hide control buttons</h1>\n<p>ColorPicker can be rendered without control buttons (Apply/Cancel). In this case, while selecting a color, the\nColorPicker pop-up is closed and selected color can be applied directly. To hide control buttons, set the <a href=\"https://help.syncfusion.com/cr/aspnetcore-blazor/Syncfusion.EJ2.Blazor~Syncfusion.EJ2.Blazor.Inputs.EjsColorPicker~ShowButtons.html\"><code class=\"language-text\">showButtons</code></a> property to <code class=\"language-text\">false</code>.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"razor\"><pre class=\"language-razor\"><code class=\"language-razor\">&lt;div class=&quot;wrapper&quot;&gt;\n    &lt;h4&gt;Choose a color&lt;/h4&gt;\n    &lt;EjsColorPicker ID=&#39;element&#39; ShowButtons=&quot;false &quot;&gt;&lt;/EjsColorPicker&gt;\n&lt;/div&gt;\n&lt;style&gt;\n    .wrapper {\n        margin: 0 auto;\n        width: 300px;\n        text-align: center;\n    }\n&lt;/style&gt;</code></pre></div>\n<p>Output be like\n<img src=\"/production/blazor/documentation/color-picker/images/hide-control.png\" alt=\"color-picker\"></p>","timeToRead":1,"excerpt":"Hide control buttons ColorPicker can be rendered without control buttons (Apply/Cancel). In this case, while selecting a color, the…","fields":{"slug":"/color-picker/how-to/hide-control-buttons/","gcse":"014729256687841406486:qzbiyd0sri4"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/color-picker/how-to/hide-control-buttons/","previous":{"html":"<h1 id=\"render-palette-alone\"><a href=\"#render-palette-alone\" aria-hidden class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Render palette alone</h1>\n<p>To render the <code class=\"language-text\">Palette</code> alone in ColorPicker, specify the <a href=\"https://help.syncfusion.com/cr/aspnetcore-blazor/Syncfusion.EJ2.Blazor~Syncfusion.EJ2.Blazor.Inputs.EjsColorPicker~Mode.html\"><code class=\"language-text\">mode</code></a> property as <code class=\"language-text\">Palette</code>, and set the <a href=\"https://help.syncfusion.com/cr/aspnetcore-blazor/Syncfusion.EJ2.Blazor~Syncfusion.EJ2.Blazor.Inputs.EjsColorPicker~ModeSwitcher.html\"><code class=\"language-text\">modeSwitcher</code></a> property to <code class=\"language-text\">false</code>.</p>\n<p>In the following sample, the <a href=\"https://help.syncfusion.com/cr/aspnetcore-blazor/Syncfusion.EJ2.Blazor~Syncfusion.EJ2.Blazor.Inputs.EjsColorPicker~ShowButtons.html\"><code class=\"language-text\">showButtons</code></a> property is disabled to hide the control buttons and it renders only the <code class=\"language-text\">Palette</code> area.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"razor\"><pre class=\"language-razor\"><code class=\"language-razor\">&lt;div class=&quot;wrapper&quot;&gt;\n    &lt;h4&gt;Choose a color&lt;/h4&gt;\n    &lt;EjsColorPicker ID=&quot;element&quot; Mode=&quot;ColorPickerMode.Palette&quot; ModeSwitcher=&quot;false&quot; ShowButtons=&quot;false&quot;&gt;&lt;/EjsColorPicker&gt;\n&lt;/div&gt;\n&lt;style&gt;\n.wrapper {\n    margin: 0 auto;\n    width: 300px;\n    text-align: center;\n    }\n&lt;/style&gt;</code></pre></div>\n<p>Output be like\n<img src=\"/production/blazor/documentation/color-picker/images/palette-alone.png\" alt=\"color-picker\"></p>\n<blockquote>\n<blockquote>\n<p>To render <code class=\"language-text\">Picker</code> alone, specify the <a href=\"https://help.syncfusion.com/cr/aspnetcore-blazor/Syncfusion.EJ2.Blazor~Syncfusion.EJ2.Blazor.Inputs.EjsColorPicker~Mode.html\"><code class=\"language-text\">mode</code></a> property as ‘Picker’.</p>\n</blockquote>\n</blockquote>","id":"66bf4e39-cda5-57ab-a2f3-08236d1b1944","fields":{"slug":"/color-picker/how-to/render-palette-alone/","parentPath":"color-picker/how-to","childPath":"render-palette-alone","gcse":"014729256687841406486:qzbiyd0sri4","header":"","breadCrumb":"ColorPicker/How To/Render palette alone","isReleaseNotes":false,"title":"How to Render palette alone in Blazor [Preview] ColorPicker component - Syncfusion","description":"Checkout and learn about Render palette alone in Blazor [Preview] ColorPicker component of Syncfusion Essential JS 2, and more details.","platform":"Blazor [Preview]","isRobots":true}},"next":{"html":"<h1 id=\"disable-colorpicker\"><a href=\"#disable-colorpicker\" aria-hidden class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Disable ColorPicker</h1>\n<p>To achieve disabled state in ColorPicker, set the <a href=\"https://help.syncfusion.com/cr/aspnetcore-blazor/Syncfusion.EJ2.Blazor~Syncfusion.EJ2.Blazor.Inputs.EjsColorPicker~Disabled.html\"><code class=\"language-text\">disabled</code></a> property to <code class=\"language-text\">true</code>. The ColorPicker pop-up cannot be accessed in disabled state.</p>\n<p>The following example shows the <code class=\"language-text\">disabled</code> state of ColorPicker component.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"razor\"><pre class=\"language-razor\"><code class=\"language-razor\">&lt;div class=&quot;wrapper&quot;&gt;\n     &lt;h4&gt;Choose a color&lt;/h4&gt;\n     &lt;EjsColorPicker ID=&quot;element&quot; Disabled=&quot;true&quot;&gt;&lt;/EjsColorPicker&gt;\n&lt;/div&gt;\n&lt;style&gt;\n.wrapper {\n    margin: 0 auto;\n    width: 300px;\n    text-align: center;\n    }\n&lt;/style&gt;</code></pre></div>\n<p>Output be like\n<img src=\"/production/blazor/documentation/color-picker/images/disable.png\" alt=\"color-picker\"></p>","id":"c52c09e2-a781-51e1-b499-51e1edcdea1e","fields":{"slug":"/color-picker/how-to/disable-color-picker/","parentPath":"color-picker/how-to","childPath":"disable-color-picker","gcse":"014729256687841406486:qzbiyd0sri4","header":"","breadCrumb":"ColorPicker/How To/Disable ColorPicker","isReleaseNotes":false,"title":"How to Disable ColorPicker in Blazor [Preview] ColorPicker component - Syncfusion","description":"Checkout and learn about Disable ColorPicker in Blazor [Preview] ColorPicker component of Syncfusion Essential JS 2, and more details.","platform":"Blazor [Preview]","isRobots":true}},"gcse":"014729256687841406486:qzbiyd0sri4","header":"","breadCrumb":"ColorPicker/How To/Hide control buttons","isReleaseNotes":false,"title":"How to Hide control buttons in Blazor [Preview] ColorPicker component - Syncfusion","description":"Checkout and learn about Hide control buttons in Blazor [Preview] ColorPicker component of Syncfusion Essential JS 2, and more details.","platform":"Blazor [Preview]","isRobots":true}}